    "body": "> But its not working anymore for some reason.\r\n\r\nSo now problem is when app is in background, even manually requested theme value is wrong.\r\n\r\nThis is nice solution: https://github.com/facebook/react-native/issues/28525#issuecomment-1041610688\r\nSo basically this weird event with wrong value gets fired when app is in background.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n- So when app is in foreground, process if theme change event is fired\r\n- When in background, ignore those events\r\n- And when app returns to foreground, manually check value",
